#-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
#
# Batch options for OAR
# =====================
#
#OAR -l nodes=2,walltime=00:30:00
#OAR -O job_%jobid%.log
#OAR -E job_%jobid%.log
#OAR -n nameandcase

#  -l, --resource=<list>              : set the requested resources for the job.
#                                       The different parameters are resource
#                                       properties registered in OAR database,
#                                       and `walltime' format is
#                                       [hour:mn:sec|hour:mn|hour].
#  -q, --queue=<queue>                : set the queue to submit the job to
#  -p, --property="<list>"            : add constraints to properties for the job.
#  -r, --reservation=<name>           : allocate resources from reservation
#  -O, --stdout=<file>                : output file name pattern
#  -E, --stderr=<file>                : error file name pattern
#  -n, --name=<jobname>               : job name
#
#-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
